Represents type Word256.

 Word256 = packed record
 case Integer of

 1 : (Words : array[0..15] of Word);
 2 : (Word32s : array[0..7] of Word32);
 3 : (Word64s : array[0..3] of Word64);
 4 : (Word128s : array[0..1] of Word128);
 end;
